# Harness primitives are version-controlled. Skills, agents, per-harness
# settings, and the repo brief are code — they ship with the repo so every
# clone and every harness (Claude Code, Codex, Pi) gets the same contract.
# Only per-run transient state under .spellbook/ is ignored.
/.spellbook/*/
!/.spellbook/repo-brief.md

